WEBVTT

00:17.517 --> 00:18.685
That’s rare.

00:20.520 --> 00:22.188
A mixed breed.

00:23.314 --> 00:26.693
Were you the one who killed Mudan?

00:26.776 --> 00:28.153
You...

00:34.117 --> 00:35.410
Bastard...

00:36.411 --> 00:40.040
I’m starting to take an interest in you.

02:14.300 --> 02:15.218
Run.

02:16.845 --> 02:19.597
I really did want to dissect you,

02:20.181 --> 02:22.684
but right now, I don’t feel
like taking anyone’s life.

02:29.107 --> 02:31.234
Fuchi-dono! Thank goodness.

02:31.317 --> 02:32.485
What's wrong?

02:32.569 --> 02:34.445
Mei’s condition...

02:35.864 --> 02:37.866
I thought it was just fatigue, but...

02:38.449 --> 02:40.076
she’s not recovering at all.

02:40.160 --> 02:42.787
Wasn't she a child at the start?

02:42.871 --> 02:44.205
What even is she?

02:44.289 --> 02:46.457
They say she’s of the same kind
as the Tensen.

02:47.959 --> 02:50.295
I also saw her use a strange power.

02:50.795 --> 02:53.214
The same kind as those monsters.

02:54.591 --> 02:56.718
Our materials are limited,

02:56.801 --> 02:59.095
but let’s make a simple fever reducer.

02:59.178 --> 03:00.680
In return, Mei,

03:01.681 --> 03:05.602
please tell us more
about yourself and the Tensen.

03:05.685 --> 03:07.312
After losing our comrades,

03:07.395 --> 03:10.064
I’ve finally realized how serious this is.

03:10.148 --> 03:13.735
Who exactly are you people,
and what is your goal?

03:13.818 --> 03:15.111
Depending on your answer,

03:15.820 --> 03:17.739
I may not be able to forgive you.

03:19.741 --> 03:20.617
Um...

03:20.700 --> 03:24.203
Hold on. We're not gonna get a proper
explanation with the way she talks, right?

03:24.287 --> 03:25.204
True.

03:25.788 --> 03:27.206
Watch your words, you two!

03:27.290 --> 03:30.209
But it’s fine. I’m used to translating.

03:30.293 --> 03:33.838
In the meanwhile, Sagi,
please work on mixing the medicine.

03:36.049 --> 03:38.134
Dragging us out to a place like this...

03:38.718 --> 03:40.720
What do you want, Gimpy-maru?

03:41.471 --> 03:43.556
My memories are back,

03:43.640 --> 03:45.683
but my combat instincts have dulled.

03:46.309 --> 03:49.979
So, I want to warm up. Humor me.

03:50.063 --> 03:53.441
So you want all of us
to come at you at once?

03:53.524 --> 03:54.609
Yeah, pretty much.

03:56.027 --> 03:58.738
You're saying you'll use me
as a practice dummy?

03:59.614 --> 04:00.865
You too.

04:01.449 --> 04:04.077
The one you hate most is me, isn’t it?

04:04.160 --> 04:05.828
If you want to kill me,
come at me with that intent.

04:07.830 --> 04:09.123
Wait a second.

04:09.207 --> 04:12.043
If you’re planning something sneaky
under cover of the chaos,

04:12.126 --> 04:13.711
I’ll cut you down.

04:13.795 --> 04:15.630
If Sensei’s in, I’m in too.

04:16.589 --> 04:19.801
Hey, woman-man, you can use your katana.

04:19.884 --> 04:21.761
I’ll beat the hell out of that bastard.

04:23.054 --> 04:25.265
The Doshi... Aza Chobe...

04:25.890 --> 04:28.518
After two battles, I’ve learned something.

04:28.601 --> 04:30.603
Relying too much
on Tao's power is dangerous.

04:31.354 --> 04:33.731
But if you can’t control it,
you won’t be able to defeat the Tensen,

04:34.399 --> 04:36.109
or anyone else, for that matter.

04:37.485 --> 04:39.529
I have to figure out how to use it.

04:44.117 --> 04:46.536
Thanks for helping.

04:47.453 --> 04:48.871
Don't underestimate me!

04:51.582 --> 04:52.750
He’s fast!

04:57.005 --> 04:58.381
Don’t track him with your eyes.

05:00.842 --> 05:02.385
Feel him with Tao.

05:11.102 --> 05:12.395
That muscle mass...

05:12.979 --> 05:15.606
Normally brute force wouldn’t work.

05:15.690 --> 05:16.858
But...

05:20.903 --> 05:22.947
If you aim for Tao’s vital points,

05:23.031 --> 05:25.199
even a weak body
can deliver a powerful blow.

05:26.367 --> 05:27.660
Wait, Nurugai!

05:29.370 --> 05:32.165
But this confirms it for me.

05:33.082 --> 05:36.169
In the realm of Tao,
it’s impossible to surpass the Tensen.

05:36.961 --> 05:40.298
They’re monsters who’ve trained
their Tao for a thousand years.

05:40.381 --> 05:42.675
Humans can’t outdo them.

05:43.509 --> 05:44.552
So then...

05:54.937 --> 05:56.981
We use the Tao that surrounds them.

05:57.648 --> 05:59.609
The stronger the force directed at you,

06:00.193 --> 06:02.153
the bigger the backlash
when you exploit it.

06:02.862 --> 06:05.406
If we can use the Tensen’s own Tao,

06:05.490 --> 06:06.908
it could become a countermeasure.

06:06.991 --> 06:07.909
Amazing!

06:08.576 --> 06:10.661
With this, we could even kill a Tensen!

06:10.745 --> 06:13.539
No, not yet. There are still
tons of challenges to solve.

06:14.332 --> 06:16.042
He’s even better than the rumors.

06:16.626 --> 06:18.920
Gabimaru might actually
be able to reach them.

06:19.504 --> 06:21.923
But is it really okay
to rely on a criminal?

06:24.634 --> 06:28.554
Gabimaru, after observing Tao,
I realized something.

06:28.638 --> 06:30.306
There are probably different types of Tao.

06:31.265 --> 06:33.434
Each type has its own
attribute and compatibility.

06:33.518 --> 06:34.560
Types?

06:34.644 --> 06:37.855
If we can make use of that,
we could even kill immortals.

06:45.113 --> 06:46.114
Huh? What do you want?

06:46.864 --> 06:48.616
You looking to fight too?

06:52.578 --> 06:54.330
What’s this supposed to be, woman-man?

06:54.914 --> 06:57.750
I know it’s shameless, but please,

06:57.834 --> 06:59.961
teach me real sword combat.

07:00.044 --> 07:01.212
Huh?

07:01.295 --> 07:02.463
Not for revenge.

07:02.547 --> 07:05.341
So I can survive here
with my own strength.

07:05.424 --> 07:07.969
You're telling me to trust
the words of a bandit?

07:15.726 --> 07:18.354
I can't prove it any other way, but...

07:18.438 --> 07:21.774
I'm serious. I don't like you,

07:21.858 --> 07:23.276
but you're stronger than me.

07:23.359 --> 07:26.362
So, teach me the sword!

07:31.993 --> 07:33.494
Do whatever you want.

07:34.245 --> 07:36.247
I was just about to swing around
a blade anyway.

07:36.330 --> 07:37.748
Bring that katana over.

07:39.542 --> 07:42.420
Even if I have to grovel in the mud,
I’ll strengthen myself.

07:42.503 --> 07:44.505
So I can fight on my own.

07:45.923 --> 07:48.259
So I can fight alongside my brother.

07:50.094 --> 07:52.346
Strength is change.

07:55.892 --> 07:58.352
We can kill them later.

07:59.020 --> 08:01.939
I’ll come save you, brother.

08:03.774 --> 08:04.817
He’s strong!

08:04.901 --> 08:07.320
He’s on a completely
different level from the Doshis.

08:08.154 --> 08:09.947
Is he the same kind as that guy?

08:15.203 --> 08:17.997
Interesting. That distorted Tao...

08:18.080 --> 08:20.208
It must have mixed
after you came to this island, right?

08:20.291 --> 08:24.086
The elixir flowers
that transform humans into Tan.

08:24.170 --> 08:28.174
Your Tao is being eroded by it,
yet you’ve maintained your sense of self.

08:28.257 --> 08:29.759
That is very rare.

08:36.849 --> 08:38.518
Let’s study you a bit more.

08:48.778 --> 08:51.697
At this rate, I don’t see a winning path,

08:51.781 --> 08:54.992
but even if I do that thing again,
there’s no guarantee I can control it.

08:55.660 --> 08:56.494
No.

08:58.955 --> 09:01.207
I don’t need guarantees.

09:01.290 --> 09:02.917
It’s do or die.

09:03.709 --> 09:06.295
It feels like roots are spreading
through my entire body.

09:06.379 --> 09:09.048
So it doesn't steal
my consciousness, I need

09:09.131 --> 09:10.716
to focus!

09:26.607 --> 09:30.403
Both his speed and power
are completely beyond human limits.

09:31.279 --> 09:33.281
My sense of self is still intact.

09:34.115 --> 09:36.409
I have to finish this fast!

09:41.289 --> 09:44.458
Your weak point is your navel, right?

09:48.004 --> 09:50.006
Oh my goodness.

09:55.886 --> 09:58.264
It really isn’t regenerating.

09:58.347 --> 10:00.516
If I destroy the navel, you die?

10:02.018 --> 10:05.271
I’m at my limit too. I have to revert.

10:09.025 --> 10:10.234
My goodness.

10:11.485 --> 10:13.904
Even after releasing the Tao
of the outer elixir flower,

10:13.988 --> 10:15.531
he’s still controlling it.

10:16.365 --> 10:18.284
This is unprecedented.

10:19.035 --> 10:21.662
So that was a decoy, huh?

10:21.746 --> 10:26.500
I only meant to scout, but I wanted
to see it with my own eyes.

10:29.545 --> 10:31.047
Beautiful.

10:32.632 --> 10:34.925
We must take him back
to the castle and study him.

10:40.723 --> 10:44.935
I’m at my limit. Any more
and my sense of self will...

10:45.519 --> 10:47.730
Don’t push yourself. You’ll die.

10:48.731 --> 10:50.441
Take care of yourself.

10:54.570 --> 10:55.905
Sleep.

11:02.119 --> 11:06.123
I know, Toma. I'm not like my father.

11:07.083 --> 11:08.292
I will come back.

11:09.085 --> 11:10.336
Collapsing...

11:12.088 --> 11:13.005
Breaking...

11:24.183 --> 11:26.060
Where am I?

11:28.354 --> 11:31.107
So you're awake, human?

11:32.983 --> 11:34.860
What the hell is this supposed to be?

11:35.361 --> 11:37.488
Your body is precious.

11:38.072 --> 11:40.574
During the process
of becoming Tan, the Taos mixed,

11:40.658 --> 11:42.868
and the human Tao prevailed.

11:42.952 --> 11:44.412
It's a miracle.

11:44.495 --> 11:46.705
I haven’t seen anything like this
in a thousand years.

11:47.206 --> 11:49.458
A man who could become

11:49.959 --> 11:52.503
the final key my research needs.

11:54.463 --> 11:56.632
What, did you suddenly
get horny or something?

11:56.715 --> 11:58.342
No, that's not it.

11:59.009 --> 12:00.386
It's the bedchamber arts.

12:00.469 --> 12:03.472
I want to circulate your Tao and mine.

12:03.973 --> 12:06.642
So I can understand it in more detail.

12:06.725 --> 12:09.395
It will also help restore
your weakened Tao.

12:09.478 --> 12:10.938
Circulate?

12:11.021 --> 12:13.107
Each Tao has different "attributes."

12:13.607 --> 12:18.237
Wood, fire, earth, metal,
and water. Five types.

12:18.320 --> 12:20.531
These attributes influence one another.

12:21.198 --> 12:24.535
By touching, you can weaken
the other’s Tao, "mutual overcoming."

12:24.618 --> 12:27.288
Or conversely, strengthen it,
"mutual generation."

12:28.747 --> 12:30.791
Hey, hey, you serious?

12:30.875 --> 12:35.129
Bedchamber arts are ineffective
without harmony between partners.

12:35.629 --> 12:36.922
Do you have any preferences?

12:37.006 --> 12:39.675
Any desired style?

12:42.678 --> 12:43.804
I do have a request.

12:44.847 --> 12:46.390
Answer my questions.

12:46.474 --> 12:50.019
What is this island?
What are you guys doing on it?

12:51.645 --> 12:54.648
According to what she said,
both the Tensen and this island

12:54.732 --> 12:57.860
were created by a single human.

12:58.444 --> 12:59.862
A human?

12:59.945 --> 13:02.615
A renowned alchemist from the continent.

13:03.616 --> 13:07.453
He researched immortality
based on Taoist philosophy.

13:07.953 --> 13:12.458
In Taoism, all phenomena
are said to be formed by Tao.

13:13.626 --> 13:14.960
On this island, he supposedly

13:15.044 --> 13:18.214
discovered a way
to directly manipulate it.

13:19.423 --> 13:22.092
By combining the Taos of living beings,

13:22.176 --> 13:23.427
grafting them together,

13:23.511 --> 13:26.889
through repeated trial and error,
he sought immortality.

13:28.265 --> 13:31.393
That’s how the Tensen were born.

13:31.977 --> 13:35.898
By fusing human and plant Tao.
They are hermaphrodites.

13:35.981 --> 13:38.609
They can strengthen Tao
through yin and yang on their own.

13:39.193 --> 13:40.402
They have been refining Tao,

13:40.486 --> 13:44.031
which is normally lost through
activity and time, for a thousand years.

13:44.990 --> 13:46.909
There is no way humans can compare.

13:47.493 --> 13:50.037
Except for one method.

13:50.913 --> 13:52.248
Tao, right?

13:52.748 --> 13:56.794
So why are these superhumans
holed up on this island?

13:58.254 --> 14:01.173
In Taoism, practices
like breathing techniques and meditation,

14:01.257 --> 14:03.842
training within one’s own body
to achieve immortality,

14:03.926 --> 14:05.511
are called "inner alchemy."

14:06.011 --> 14:09.056
On the other hand, methods
that allow anyone to become immortal,

14:09.139 --> 14:11.600
regardless of constitution or training,

14:11.684 --> 14:14.478
like trying to create a medicine for it,

14:14.562 --> 14:16.230
are called "outer alchemy."

14:16.313 --> 14:19.191
This is what the Tensen are creating.

14:19.275 --> 14:20.818
- What?
- That means...

14:20.901 --> 14:22.069
The elixir!

14:22.152 --> 14:24.154
So it really exists?

14:24.238 --> 14:26.323
It’s still under research, apparently.

14:26.407 --> 14:30.327
What they call "Tan"
are prototype test products.

14:30.411 --> 14:32.830
They gather human lives like honey

14:32.913 --> 14:36.750
and efficiently absorb their Tao,
otherwise known as their life force.

14:37.418 --> 14:41.714
It's like taking someone else's lifespan
and adding it to your own.

14:42.923 --> 14:46.093
The Tensen extend
their lives with Tan as well.

14:46.176 --> 14:48.721
Their self-sustaining Tao
isn’t perfect, either.

14:49.221 --> 14:52.600
So if they lose a large amount
of Tao in a short time,

14:52.683 --> 14:53.726
they die.

14:54.602 --> 14:58.606
But the amount of Tan
they have now is still enough, isn't it?

14:58.689 --> 15:01.692
Once they complete a method
that can make anyone immortal,

15:01.775 --> 15:02.860
what do they plan to do?

15:03.986 --> 15:05.446
I don’t know.

15:05.529 --> 15:08.616
Probably the will of Alchemist Shufu.

15:08.699 --> 15:10.284
- Shu...
- Who?

15:10.367 --> 15:14.079
The alchemist who created
the Tensen and this island.

15:14.163 --> 15:15.205
Shufu...

15:15.289 --> 15:17.917
That is, Xu Fu.

15:18.000 --> 15:20.753
In the Qin era,
he served the First Emperor,

15:20.836 --> 15:22.504
and in pursuit of immortality,

15:22.588 --> 15:25.257
with 3,000 youths and a hundrd artisans,

15:25.341 --> 15:27.343
he set out into the eastern seas.

15:27.426 --> 15:29.720
He was never seen again.

15:29.803 --> 15:32.264
A figure from over a thousand years ago.

15:32.348 --> 15:33.724
They say he’s still
somewhere on the island,

15:33.807 --> 15:36.226
continuing his research.

15:36.310 --> 15:39.355
This place is both a laboratory
and an experimental ground.

15:39.939 --> 15:45.986
A miniature garden to create and observe
immortal life.

15:48.238 --> 15:53.035
So all those monsters
were artificially created?

15:53.118 --> 15:54.536
That's right.

15:54.620 --> 15:57.164
Each has an experimental purpose.

15:57.873 --> 16:01.293
The wooden people exist
to observe the lives of immortals.

16:01.377 --> 16:05.547
They lack a strong concept of death,
so the Soshin exist to teach them morality

16:05.631 --> 16:07.758
and maintain order.

16:08.676 --> 16:11.929
We, too, are merely creations.

16:13.013 --> 16:16.183
Born from the fusion of the master’s Tao
and the Tao of flowers.

16:16.767 --> 16:19.311
One being, yet also separate.

16:19.395 --> 16:22.398
A family of myself.

16:23.190 --> 16:25.275
You can do it all this easily?

16:25.359 --> 16:28.904
It is not easy. Tao is the source of life...

16:28.988 --> 16:31.490
No, the source of everything.

16:31.573 --> 16:33.951
It fills the world like dust,

16:34.034 --> 16:36.161
shaping all that exists.

16:36.245 --> 16:37.913
Even that incense,

16:37.997 --> 16:41.375
and the air, are forms of Tao.

16:41.458 --> 16:45.796
Therefore, to manipulate Tao
is to manipulate the laws of the world.

16:45.879 --> 16:50.300
But unlike inanimate objects,
controlling life is difficult.

16:52.302 --> 16:55.556
That’s why your Tao is so valuable.

16:55.639 --> 16:57.558
I want to study it.

16:57.641 --> 17:00.019
So you’ll use me for research

17:00.102 --> 17:03.313
and turn every human
on this island into an elixir?

17:03.397 --> 17:05.065
No, that's not it.

17:05.816 --> 17:07.818
All humans on the mainland.

17:07.901 --> 17:09.319
What?

17:09.903 --> 17:12.531
The preparations are already complete.

17:12.614 --> 17:14.825
All that’s left is the perfect Tan.

17:14.908 --> 17:18.662
If you cooperate,
we'll accept you as one of us.

17:18.746 --> 17:20.080
Not as Tan,

17:20.164 --> 17:23.083
but as a companion
who pursues the Tao to its limits.

17:24.835 --> 17:27.588
What’s the smartest choice here?

17:27.671 --> 17:32.217
In my current state, I can’t beat her.
Even escaping would be tough.

17:32.301 --> 17:35.471
So what should I prioritize?

17:42.269 --> 17:44.229
I'll do the bedchamber art.

17:44.313 --> 17:47.566
If it lets me master the Tao.

17:47.649 --> 17:50.986
But I'm not into girls riding me.

17:51.070 --> 17:54.364
Don’t worry. I’ll be gentle.

17:54.948 --> 17:58.118
Don’t resist the situation, adapt to it.

17:58.202 --> 18:01.622
Adapt... and then swallow it whole.

18:02.539 --> 18:04.374
Just wait, Toma.

18:05.626 --> 18:08.754
As expected... such wonderful Tao.

18:10.881 --> 18:14.635
In other words, that Xu Fu guy
is the root of everything.

18:16.553 --> 18:17.846
- Whoa!
- What's this?

18:18.555 --> 18:21.517
What is going on?

18:22.101 --> 18:25.437
My body is incomplete.

18:26.230 --> 18:29.775
When I use Tao,
the tree transformation advances.

18:29.858 --> 18:32.236
I can’t recover on my own.

18:32.319 --> 18:35.197
Then, if we restore your Tao,
like Gabimaru did...

18:35.280 --> 18:36.156
No.

18:37.074 --> 18:40.285
Too little. The circulation isn’t enough.

18:40.369 --> 18:45.541
Because my dantian,
or ovule, was destroyed by Rien.

18:45.624 --> 18:46.917
Rien?

18:47.000 --> 18:48.669
Rien and I

18:48.752 --> 18:52.798
were the first disciples
created by Master Shufu.

18:53.423 --> 18:55.551
But Rien changed.

18:56.802 --> 19:00.222
For the sake of outer alchemy,
she killed many.

19:08.689 --> 19:10.149
I couldn’t stop her.

19:11.066 --> 19:14.111
I fled Horai.

19:16.280 --> 19:18.157
So it was true after all.

19:20.033 --> 19:22.452
At this rate, Mei will...

19:22.536 --> 19:25.330
- You should use my Tao.
- What?

19:25.414 --> 19:28.750
The Tensen can freely manipulate Tao.

19:28.834 --> 19:30.919
They should be able to extract Tao

19:31.003 --> 19:33.714
from living beings and make it their own.

19:33.797 --> 19:35.215
They can do something like that?

19:36.175 --> 19:38.051
But then, you would--

19:38.135 --> 19:39.344
It's okay.

19:41.180 --> 19:44.391
Mei, I'm going to turn
into a tree soon anyway.

19:45.559 --> 19:48.312
And this is atonement.

19:48.395 --> 19:49.229
Atonement?

19:49.313 --> 19:52.608
I met her several hundred years ago.

19:52.691 --> 19:55.777
I had a wife and a daughter.

19:55.861 --> 19:58.780
Both of them turned
into trees before I did.

19:59.281 --> 20:02.159
The villagers gradually followed,

20:02.242 --> 20:04.453
and I was left alone.

20:05.120 --> 20:07.956
And then, the time finally came.

20:15.964 --> 20:18.217
She just happened to be
about the same age.

20:19.301 --> 20:20.719
That’s all.

20:20.802 --> 20:22.846
But she looked like my daughter.

20:22.930 --> 20:26.058
My... young daughter.

20:28.560 --> 20:29.811
I knew the truth.

20:30.687 --> 20:34.316
That she was something unnatural.

20:34.399 --> 20:37.861
That she truly wanted to leave the island.

20:39.029 --> 20:41.073
I ignored all of it

20:41.615 --> 20:44.826
and kept playing house.

20:44.910 --> 20:46.703
Please forgive me.

20:46.787 --> 20:50.290
I didn't see you. I saw my daughter.

20:51.416 --> 20:52.960
For hundreds of years,

20:53.043 --> 20:56.129
I made you cling to my lies and regrets.

20:56.213 --> 20:57.839
This is my one chance to atone.

20:57.923 --> 21:00.759
Please, use my life!

21:04.680 --> 21:06.265
It wasn’t a lie.

21:06.765 --> 21:09.685
We really felt like a family.

21:12.354 --> 21:14.189
Like a parent and child.

21:41.091 --> 21:43.844
Goodbye, dad.

23:18.313 --> 23:20.065
Miss!

23:20.148 --> 23:22.317
Did you shrink again?

23:22.400 --> 23:24.486
Well, I get the situation, but still!

23:24.569 --> 23:27.197
If I’m being honest,

23:27.280 --> 23:29.116
I wanted to carry you
on my shoulders the way you were!

23:29.199 --> 23:31.827
Shut up. Is this really
something to lose it over?

23:31.910 --> 23:34.287
You’ll understand when you grow up, kid!

23:34.371 --> 23:36.790
You’re really going to learn
swordsmanship from that guy?

23:39.042 --> 23:41.128
Looks like your wound has closed.

23:41.211 --> 23:43.130
It might leave a scar, though.

23:43.213 --> 23:44.047
Thank you--

23:44.131 --> 23:45.841
No need to thank me. I don't trust you.

23:48.218 --> 23:50.470
Everyone, don't stop
what you're doing. Just listen.

23:50.554 --> 23:51.763
- Sensei.
- Sensei.

23:51.847 --> 23:55.725
After discussing things with Gabimaru,
we've decided what to do next, but...

23:55.809 --> 23:58.854
Hey, Kitty-maru,
why are you the one deciding?

23:58.937 --> 24:00.397
I’m more suited than you are.

24:00.480 --> 24:02.232
What? Don’t get cocky, you bastard!

24:02.315 --> 24:05.110
Honestly, what a disorganized bunch.

24:07.028 --> 24:07.988
What’s wrong?

24:09.322 --> 24:10.740
Someone is here.

24:11.324 --> 24:14.369
From the sea. It's really big.

24:14.995 --> 24:16.621
It's a lot of Tao.

24:16.705 --> 24:17.998
You mean a large group?

24:18.081 --> 24:21.001
I don’t know, but...

24:23.086 --> 24:25.046
it's really strong.

24:25.130 --> 24:26.798
Subtitle translation by: Maslin Friedman
